channel.title: Felt like playing
channel.description:
Decided to log on today and play some runescape (as i was sick, felt in the mood at the time)
I have a character lv 50, with 2.5m on it, 68 woodcut.
Also have an archer with all 1's except 61 ranged, has 9m on him.
What character do i play? what should i do?
( iwent and brought 1k law runes and started spamming varrock teleport on my archer, got boring fast )
They are non member, i felt like fletching at the time.
